channel.title: Rsmv
channel.description:
I just recently had the urge to design my own characters using RSVM to get all of the models. just one problem. I go to Main.java, change the version to 660, compile, and when i hit run, it does this...
C:\Users\*****\Desktop\RSVM>java Main Runescape Model Grabber Thanks to Silabsoft ~~~~~~~~~~ Grabbing Cache Version. Trying: 660 Accepted. ~~~~~~~~~~ Sending request for Model: 1 Model Grabbing Complete C:\Users\Tyler\Desktop\RSVM>pause Press any key to continue . . .
lol then on top of that, the model folder is still empty. Any Solutions?
